{"tid":2175900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共公告禁其實彈軍演位置 警告美軍勿擅自闖入","createTime":"2020-08-26T18:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T18:15:55.000Z","uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7139d586ceb48230042feddda2d995a7479d8684","tid":2175900,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:03:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">共軍27日起在東海武器訓練 距離台灣約467公里</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/08/26 22:29<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200826/3000x3203_836466188212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200826%2F3000x3203_836466188212.jpg&h=76daa163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共軍自22日開始，陸續在渤海、黃海、東海和南海實施軍演。（中央社製圖）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北26日電）中國海事局官網今天的公告顯示，<strong>共軍將於8月27日8時至30日下午6時在東海海域進行「武器訓練」，期間禁止船隻駛入連線水域範圍。初步檢視公布座標位置，訓練範圍距離台灣約467公里。</strong><br />\n<br />\n根據公告，共軍這次進行「實際使用武器訓練」範圍為：29&deg;35'30&quot;N、122&deg;54'00&quot;E；29&deg;35'30&quot;N、123&deg;18'00&quot;E；29&deg;57'30&quot;N、123&deg;18'00&quot;E；29&deg;57'30&quot;N、123&deg;55'00&quot;E；29&deg;06'30&quot;N、123&deg;55'00&quot;E；29&deg;06'30&quot;N、122&deg;54'00&quot;E。<br />\n<br />\n自8月22日開始，共軍陸續在渤海、黃海、東海和南海實施軍演。中國江蘇省連雲港海事局昨天公告，<strong>25日至27日每天上午8時至傍晚6時，於黃海南部進行實彈射擊，禁止船隻駛入。</strong><br />\n<br />\n山東海事局、海南海事局官網日前先後通報，解放軍於22日至26日、24日至29日，分別在青島至連雲港以東黃海海域、海南島東南部南海海域進行實彈軍事演習活動。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中國海事局21日也宣布，<strong>8月24日至9月30日，在渤海海域執行超過一個月的實彈射擊活動，期間禁止船舶駛入。</strong>（編輯：繆宗翰/楊昇儒）1090826<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200826/5019x3346_901511337386.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200826%2F5019x3346_901511337386.jpg&h=79bd3c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n共軍將於27日8時至30日下午6時在東海海域進行「武器訓練」，期間禁止船隻駛入連線水域範圍。圖為共軍過去演習情形。（中新社）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202008260206.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202008260206.aspx&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=a871dc29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202008260206.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"00f82f36491d053256f836fcc4c2761b9b497e2f","tid":2175900,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:04:20.000Z","msg":"後果很嚴重<br />\n後果自負"},{"pid":"de14df8a52e7247f617bf54d8c10b13397ca7d93","tid":2175900,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:05:39.000Z","msg":"共軍在南海試射 港媒：應為東風21D與東風26飛彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Z9vbj_aYMgdUxst9SNri0OW2D6w=/1204x784/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CVUGCOMRHVA4ZMWA2FVP37C7DU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ9vbj_aYMgdUxst9SNri0OW2D6w%3D%2F1204x784%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCVUGCOMRHVA4ZMWA2FVP37C7DU.jpg&h=cc8c82a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA DF-26 missile was from Qinghai into the South China Sea on Tuesday, according to a source close to the Chinese military. Photo: Reuters<br />\n圖片來源 : 路透<br />\n台灣空域近日首見美、中、台偵查機同時現蹤，美國U-2高空偵察機25日一度闖入中國解放軍北部戰區實彈演習禁飛區活動，引發中國國防部抗議指控「挑釁」。解放軍今（26日）又在南海進行反艦彈道飛彈試射，美軍出動追蹤導彈的RC-135S偵察機從巴士海峽往南海進行偵搜。香港《南華早報》指稱，共軍發射的是「東風26」與「東風21D」飛彈，主要目的就是給美國警告。<br />\n<br />\n關注中國軍事發展的法國網站「East Pendulum」在推特發文指，解放軍26日早上從兩個不同的基地向南海試射反艦彈道飛彈。另有消息稱，試射的相信為有「航母殺手」之稱的東風21D及東風26，分別從浙江寧波，以及青海大柴旦行政區發射，兩枚飛彈的落點都在海南島與西沙群島之間的海域，先前海南省海事局已經預告本周一至周六將有實彈演習。<br />\n<br />\n東風26射程可達4千公里，可搭載傳統彈頭或核子彈頭。東風21射程約在1800公里，中國報導聲稱21D是東風21系列中最新進的一款。<br />\n<br />\n香港《南華早報》引述消息人士指，解放軍今早的試射，是回應美國近期不斷對中國的偵察行動，包括周二（25日）派出U-2高空偵察機闖入解放軍渤海實彈演習的禁飛區。<br />\n<br />\n消息又指，解放軍想通過試射，阻嚇其他想介入南海爭議的勢力，「中國是回應美軍機艦不斷增加在南海的活動，但中國不想鄰國誤會了北京的意圖」。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述一名軍事評論員表示，美國不斷測試中國對台灣及南海的底線，迫使中國向華盛頓展示可以阻止美軍航空母艦進入南海的軍事實力。（國際中心╱綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200827/E6OBO6ZLORET7BCEC2OSZGZT6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200827%2FE6OBO6ZLORET7BCEC2OSZGZT6U%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=a04e6823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200827%2FE6OBO6ZLORET7BCEC2OSZGZT6U%2F&h=1f8d65e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200827/E6OBO6ZLORET7BCEC2OSZGZT6U/</a>"},{"pid":"5c70375e6338cf95b6b89f9e1b2b29a480b71190","tid":2175900,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:06:01.000Z","msg":"無公佈位置，就算美軍闖入左，中共都可以否認"},{"pid":"be086ce56e0144d3d6e1eba7021f71e31d659173","tid":2175900,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"中共公告<span class=\"red\">近期</span>實彈軍演位置 警告美軍勿擅自闖入<br />\n<br />\n抱歉！注音符號輸入錯誤"},{"pid":"4c10269772349138b8c09f0400d477c3fcfd4ea2","tid":2175900,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"南海係國際海域都射導彈<br />\n開咗個頭就等睇美軍開始炸南海<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c72fbbbc2ec266d935e8d6e434a82b16e47310","tid":2175900,"uid":287751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>借個位 請幫推<br />\n831 有行動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">【行動 Post 請置頂】八三一週年，手足歸隊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2175581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"735be7781d9ac689822b7f7028f661b0026c2426","tid":2175900,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c10269772349138b8c09f0400d477c3fcfd4ea2","tid":2175900,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:08:21.000Z","msg":"南海係國際海域都射導彈<br />\n開咗個頭就等睇美軍開始炸南海<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n川普正想在南海開戰"},{"pid":"7fc96c14b6e0eb8ee29deea3ffb857097e0b935d","tid":2175900,"uid":46966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />射落海? 屌你係個度打個飛機美軍仲撚驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afff2879a9e05cf45b62b689a16c70e229a1a08","tid":2175900,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:15:54.000Z","msg":"雖遠必豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a8333b689ebcd2275b54adcaaf14c2d4a203f5","tid":2175900,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"留名睇美國當冇事發生"}]}